data.description: SUMMER SPECIAL: NEW LOWER PRICE PLUS $1500 SELLER CREDIT TOWARDS NEW APPLIANCES!!  BEST PRICED TILE ROOF AND SPACIOUS HOME IN SOLIVITA! New construction for this size starts at $279,000!  Enjoy our beautiful Florida sunshine in one of the most highly rated active resort-style 55+ communities right in the heart of Kissimmee!  2 Golf courses, several pools, tennis & basketball courts, lake access to boat & fish, a clubhouse, activities & sooooo much more to enjoy!! Beautifully designed and organized.  Feel at peace & at home in this 24 hour gated community with exterior maintenance & cable included, golf carts are welcome, & residents are encouraged to enjoy all the outdoors.  Private local shopping, restaurants, pharmacy, hospital and entertainment within minutes of your home.    This spacious home sits on an oversized lot, has 2 masters plus a separate den or flex space to use for whatever your heart desires, a formal dining room, formal living room, & a great room with the kitchen, family room and breakfast nook overlooking the back yard retreat. You'll have easy maintenance tile throughout all the living areas, large laundry room, a full size 2 car garage for your golf carts & vehicles, & a long driveway for added privacy & space for guests.  The large covered screened in porch is great outdoor space too!  Solivita offers a fitness & wellness program, car shows, classes, a monthly newsletter, & different clubs for excitement all year round!   Whether you're a snow bird who needs a place of your own to land for half the year or you're ready to call Florida your permanent home, this is the place to be!   With home prices still on the rise, its the best time to purchase & take advantage of all-time low interest rates! Your retirement is waiting!  Call to make this fantastic home yours now!
data.whatILove: 55 PLUS COMMUNITY! ALSO A TWO GOLF COURSE COMMUNITY! This attractive home is the "Bach" model which features a 2nd bedroom with a full bath. The oversized ac is about 4 years old and there is a new hot water heater and heavy duty garbage disposal. Tile throughout except for the 2 bedrooms & den which has brand new carpet. The master bath has a tub and separate shower & double sinks. There are 6 ceiling fans with one in the lanai and one in the garage. The home sits on an oversized lot & has a 16x13 enclosed lanai. The seller has planted 3 nice trees in the back and a nice new palm tree in the front. There is a sprinkler system. A large heated community pool is about a half block away and the charming town of Solivita is only a mile and a half away. They recently opened a new pharmacy there and 2 new restaurants and a coffee shop as well as many other restaurants & shopsl. Other amenities include an indoor olympic size pool, tennis & basketball courts, baseball, a cushioned running track and lake access to rent a boat & fish. The seller says "If you can think of it, they have it" He also says that the lakes are loaded with bass. The entire area of Solivita is lovely with lush trees and beautiful landscaping, calming lakes and sidewalks to walk your dog. This is a golf cart community!  Your monthly fees cover all of these amenities except for golf. You get free basic cable, outside maintenance including landscaping. Make your appointment to this lovely home today!
